HEADWORD: Servable
<hw>Serv"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Serve</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Capable of being
served.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[L. <ets>servabilis</ets>.]</ety> <def>Capable of
being preserved.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Servage</ent>⟦br⟧
